Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: USA, Cuba, and Guantanamo Bay
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yljmg
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 26 Aug 1994
The US role in the Cuban War of Independence and how America is housing Cuban refugees in the Guantanamo Bay facility are considered by Alistair Cooke.